{"type": "article", "id": 2219, "title": "Wallpaper 2014 设计大奖 Unam 座椅", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:51:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222256NED8R9rU5Zfjb6n0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tUNAM FOR VERY WOOD BY GERVASONI <br>\r\n德国年轻设计师 Sebastian Herkner<a href=\"http://www.sebastianherkner.com/\"></a> 为意大利家具制造商 Very Wood by Gervasoni 设计的 Unam 椅子有多种尺寸版本，既可以作为餐椅搭配餐桌，也可以作为休闲椅放置在家里的任何一个角落。椅子的框架部分全部用实木作为材料，线条简洁流畅，前后脚的支撑结构带有复古的韵味，户外版本的椅子用防水绳编织作为椅背，还新增多种撞色搭配的色彩供选择。这把休闲椅获得了 Wallpaper 2014 设计大奖。<a href=\"http://www.archiproducts.com/en/products/135853/unam-upholstered-wooden-chair-unam-chair-very-wood.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135054EXscIYST5i8N4RWD.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135057Ag36yRDpG9KIfd1N.jpeg\" width=\"640\" height=\"478\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74739583\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135058Ipaq9D0tGbZReu2o.jpeg\" width=\"640\" height=\"478\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74739583\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135059gmp6iWx0cI8E9sDS.jpeg\" width=\"640\" height=\"478\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74739583\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}